ci_support_linux_64_python3.10.____cpyth:
c_compiler:
- gcc
c_compiler_version:
- '14'
c_stdlib:
- sysroot
c_stdlib_version:
- '2.17'
channel_sources:
- conda-forge
channel_targets:
- conda-forge main
docker_image:
- quay.io/condaforge/linux-anvil-x86_64:alma9
pin_run_as_build:
  python:
    min_pin: x.x
    max_pin: x.x
python:
- 3.10.* *_cpython
target_platform:
- linux-64
name: python-librt
raw_meta_yaml:
# yaml-language-server: $schema=https://raw.githubusercontent.com/prefix-dev/recipe-format/main/schema.json
schema_version: 1

context:
  version: "0.8.0"

package:
  name: python-librt
  version: ${{ version }}

source:
  - url: https://pypi.org/packages/source/l/librt/librt-${{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: cb74cdcbc0103fc988e04e5c58b0b31e8e5dd2babb9182b6f9490488eb36324b

build:
  number: 0
  script:
    - ${{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv --no-deps --no-build-isolation --disable-pip-version-check

requirements:
  build:
    - ${{ compiler("c") }}
    - ${{ stdlib("c") }}
    - if: build_platform != target_platform
      then:
        - cross-python_${{ target_platform }}
        - python
  host:
    - pip
    - python
    - setuptools >=77.0.3
  run:
    - python

tests:
  - python:
      imports: librt
      pip_check: true
  - files:
      source:
        - smoke_tests.py
    requirements:
      run:
        - mypy_extensions
        - pytest
    script:
      - pytest -vv --tb=long --color=yes smoke_tests.py

about:
  homepage: https://pypi.org/project/librt
  repository: https://github.com/mypyc/librt
  summary: Mypyc runtime library
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - bollwyvl
    - conda-forge/mypy
